text:
The spirit smiles for a moment, as if pleased. He composes himself, standing with one hand behind him as he begins to speak in a soft, lilting tone:

"Suiang jianne shyr nan bye yih nan;
"Dong feng wu lih bay hua tsarn;
"Chuen tsarn daw syy sy fang jinn;
"Lah Jiuh cherng huei ley shyy gan."

That being said, he appears content to stand and wait patiently for your reply.

You open your mouth to voice a question, but before you can begin the spirit begins to speak in a soft, lilting tone:

"Suiang jianne shyr nan bye yih nan;
"Dong feng wu lih bay hua tsarn;
"Chuen tsarn daw syy sy fang jinn;
"Lah Jiuh cherng huei ley shyy gan."

That being said, he appears content to stand and wait patiently for your reply.

